&lt;h2 class="text-amber-500 text-3xl my-6" id="-solución-de-problemas">
⚠️ Solución de Problemas
&lt;a href="#-soluci%c3%b3n-de-problemas" class="text-gray-500">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 class="text-gray-500 text-3xl my-6" id="selinux-está-bloqueando-mi-aplicación">
&amp;ldquo;SELinux está bloqueando mi aplicación&amp;rdquo;
&lt;a href="#selinux-est%c3%a1-bloqueando-mi-aplicaci%c3%b3n" class="text-gray-500">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Identificar el error:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo grep &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;avc: denied&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /var/log/audit/audit.log
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Solución temporal (solo para pruebas):&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo setenforce &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Solución permanente:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># Usar las recomendaciones de sealert&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo sealert -l &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;*&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> grep -A &lt;span class="m">10&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Sugerencia&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
